      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and it shows in every square inch. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero swirls, stone chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear bolsters or creasing, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history documenting every oil change and inspection performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. With remarkably low mileage and a chassis that has never seen salt or inclement weather, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly pristine example of automotive excellence. Needs nothing but a new garage to call home.",
